Amy Brandon Thomas https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amy_Brandon_Thomas 0 Amy Marguerite Brandon Thomas (9 March 1890 – 6 May 1974) was an English film and stage actress. She was the daughter of the playwright Brandon Thomas. She is also known as Amy Brandon-Thomas. Amy_Marguerite_Brandon_Thomas ( 9_March_1890 – 6_May_1974 ) was an_English_film_and_stage_actress .
